   <text>
      <body divRole="original-translation">
         <div type="original" xml:lang="nl">
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.1" f="1r" facs="#s1r" n="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.1" n="1">Mei.<ptr type="note" target="#note.orig.nl.1"/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.2" n="2">Beste J.,</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.3" n="3">Hoe zeer ’t mij spijt, ik kan geen afspraak maken, ik ben onzeker van mijn tijd. Tenminste de eerste dagen, misschien op ’t eind der week zal ik je even schrijven.</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.4" n="4" rend="indent">Je bent toch vrij zooals gezegd.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.5" n="5">Salut.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.1"
                corresp="#pb.orig.nl.1"
                f="1r"
                facs="#s1r"
                n="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.1" corresp="#p.orig.nl.1" n="1">May.<ptr type="note" target="#note.tr.en.1"/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.2" corresp="#p.orig.nl.2" n="2">Dear J.,</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.3" corresp="#p.orig.nl.3" n="3">Much as it disappoints me I can’t make an appointment, I’m not sure about my time. At least for the next few days, perhaps at the end of the week, I’ll drop you a line.</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.4" corresp="#p.orig.nl.4" n="4" rend="indent">You’re free after all, as you’ve said. </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.5" corresp="#p.orig.nl.5" n="5">Salut.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
